== 發行 ==
《救命解藥》最先於2016年12月10日在{{le|Butt-Numb-A-Thon|Butt-Numb-A-Thon}}上首映。

電影最初定於2016年9月23日在美國上映，後來發行日改至2017年2月17日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=acureforwellness.htm |title=A Cure for Wellness (2016) |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2015-05-07 |accessdate=2016-05-28 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906115742/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=acureforwellness.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]（MPAA）將本片評為「R級」。2016年10月19日，釋出首支電影預告<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mcVodJmBlU |title=A Cure for Wellness Official Trailer [HD] 20th Century FOX |publisher=Youtube |date=2016-10-19 |accessdate=2016-10-20 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020110644/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mcVodJmBlU&gl=US&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《救命解藥》在影評人間的評價褒貶不一，影評人主要稱讚該片的視覺畫面、演出和野心，但也批評電影的劇情結構與過長的片長<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bumbray|first1=Chris|title=Review: A Cure for Wellness|url=http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/review-a-cure-for-wellness-243|website=JoBlo|publisher=JoBlo Media Inc.|accessdate=8 February 2017|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155846/http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/review-a-cure-for-wellness-243|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據162條評論，新鮮度42%，平均得分5.3／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_cure_for_wellness|title=A Cure for Wellness (2017)|work=爛番茄|accessdate=2017-06-09|archive-date=2017-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608160737/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_cure_for_wellness|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分47，代表「好壞平均參雜的評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/a-cure-for-wellness|title=A Cure for Wellness reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2017-06-09|archive-date=2017-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170607095831/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/a-cure-for-wellness|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，《救命解藥》與同期上映的《[[長城_(電影)|長城]]》和《{{le|徒手大戰|Fist Fight}}》共同競爭，估計於首週末能從兩千七百多間戲院中獲得600萬至800萬美元左右的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-great-wall-20170213-story.html |title=Matt Damon's 'Great Wall' poised for soft U.S. opening against 'Lego Batman' and 'Fifty Shades' |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=2017-02-17 |archive-date=2017-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214235252/http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-great-wall-20170213-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="preview2">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/fifty-shades-darker-lego-batman-great-wall-cure-for-wellness-fist-fight-box-office-1201912117/|title=Moviegoers Likely To Spend Less George Washingtons Over Presidents Day Weekend: Box Office Preview|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2017-02-17|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216191928/http://deadline.com/2017/02/fifty-shades-darker-lego-batman-great-wall-cure-for-wellness-fist-fight-box-office-1201912117/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房總計僅420萬美元，位居當週票房排名第十，口碑不佳<ref name="opening">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/lego-batman-fifty-shades-fist-fight-the-great-wall-cure-for-wellness-weekend-box-office-1201914695/ |title=Holdovers Reign Over Holiday Weekend, But Why Did The New Releases Tank?: Presidents’ Day B.O. |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2017-02-20 |archive-date=2017-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219235941/http://deadline.com/2017/02/lego-batman-fifty-shades-fist-fight-the-great-wall-cure-for-wellness-weekend-box-office-1201914695/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

